{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"Cuando el Sol se contraiga [y oscurezca],","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:2","price":"cuando las estrellas pierdan su luz,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:3","price":"cuando las montañas sean pulverizadas,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:4","price":"cuando las camellas preñadas sean dejadas de lado,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"las camellas preñadas: Imagen que representa la gravedad de la situación, ya que por su preocupación las personas abandonan aquellas cosas que les son muy preciadas. ","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:5","price":"cuando las bestias salvajes sean acorraladas,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:6","price":"cuando los mares hiervan y se desborden,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:7","price":"cuando las almas vuelvan a emparejarse [con sus cuerpos],","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:8","price":"cuando se le pregunte a las niñas que fueron enterradas vivas","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:9","price":"por qué pecado las mataron,","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"Los árabes en la época preislámica enterraban a sus hijas vivas por temor a la pobreza o a que estas pudieran caer en manos de los enemigos y eso trajera deshonra a su familia. ","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:10","price":"cuando los registros [de las obras] sean repartidos,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:11","price":"cuando la bóveda celeste desaparezca,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:12","price":"cuando el fuego del Infierno sea avivado,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:13","price":"y cuando el Paraíso sea acercado.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:14","price":"En ese momento sabrá cada alma el resultado de sus obras.","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:15","price":"Juro por los astros","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:16","price":"que recorren sus órbitas,","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:17","price":"y [juro] por la noche cuando extiende su oscuridad,","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:18","price":"y [juro] por la mañana cuando extiende su luminosidad,","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:19","price":"que [el Corán] es la palabra [de Dios transmitida] por un emisario noble,","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"un emisario noble: El ángel Gabriel.","lang":"es"},{"name":"81:20","price":"dotado de poder y distinción ante el Señor del Trono.","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:21","price":"El obedecido [por otros ángeles] y el digno confidente [de la revelación].","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:22","price":"[Sepan que] su compañero [el Profeta Mujámmad] no es un loco,","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:23","price":"lo vio [al ángel Gabriel] en el horizonte claro,","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:24","price":"no oculta nada de lo que le fue revelado.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:25","price":"[El Corán] no es la palabra de un demonio maldito.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:26","price":"¿A dónde irán [con ese argumento]?","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:27","price":"[El Corán] es un Mensaje para toda la humanidad,","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:28","price":"para que se encamine quien quiera.","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"81:29","price":"Pero sepan que solo se encaminará quien quiera Dios, Señor del universo.","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"]}